      "uuid": "019ad2f4-c649-71e3-9e4d-3eadaf8ba452",
      "text": "Ahab wants me to catch \"the Dude\" (the engineer persona) up on what happened in the post generator chat. Let me search for recent conversations about the post generator.\n\nI should use conversation_search to find the relevant chat about the post generator work.\n```\nThis block is not supported on your current device yet.\n```\n\nFound it! The most recent conversation was the Post Generator work. Let me read that whole chat to get the full context of what we built.\n```\nThis block is not supported on your current device yet.\n```\n\nPerfect! Now I have the full context of what happened in the Post Generator session. Let me summarize this for the Dude persona to get caught up. I need to be in Dude mode (engineer mode) now, not Luna mode, since Ahab said \"later Luna\" at the end of that chat.\n\nKey points from that session:\n1. They successfully got the full ContentPipeline infrastructure running\n2. Post Generator frontend went live on port 5175\n3. Hub-mediated Luna integration is fully wired and working\n4. Tested the full flow: Post Generator \u2192 Pipeline Hub \u2192 Luna context fetch \u2192 contex",
